		<title>How to import contacts?</title>
		<link>https://docs.chatrace.com/kb/import-contacts/</link>
					<comments>https://docs.chatrace.com/kb/import-contacts/#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Team]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2019 03:36:31 +0000</pubDate>
				<guid isPermaLink="false">https://docs.chatrace.com/?post_type=kb&#038;p=242</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[The &#8216;Import Contact&#8217; tool is powerful and allows you to import contacts into your Chatrace account. With this tool, you can easily import WhatsApp contacts,]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>The &#8216;Import Contact&#8217; tool is powerful and allows you to import contacts into your Chatrace account. With this tool, you can easily import WhatsApp contacts, SMS contacts and also import contacts from other chatbot platforms.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper">
<iframe loading="lazy" title="How to import Sms and Whatsapp contact" width="780" height="439" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/TTCJteDWx84?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe>
</div></figure>



<p>To Import Contact, go to the &#8216;Contact&#8217; section and click on action >> Import contacts.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="558" src="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-20_234550279-1024x558.png" alt="" class="wp-image-2740" srcset="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-20_234550279-1024x558.png 1024w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-20_234550279-300x163.png 300w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-20_234550279-768x418.png 768w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-20_234550279-1536x837.png 1536w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-20_234550279.png 1920w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading">Import contacts from other chatbot platforms</h4>



<p><strong>To imports contacts from Manychat, Select Manychat on the source option</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="498" src="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-20_235027463-1024x498.png" alt="" class="wp-image-2741" srcset="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-20_235027463-1024x498.png 1024w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-20_235027463-300x146.png 300w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-20_235027463-768x373.png 768w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-20_235027463-1536x747.png 1536w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-20_235027463.png 1903w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<p><strong>To import contacts from other chatbot platforms different from Manychat, set the source as Other messenger bot platform and upload PSIDs</strong></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="498" src="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-20_235519809-1024x498.png" alt="" class="wp-image-2742" srcset="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-20_235519809-1024x498.png 1024w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-20_235519809-300x146.png 300w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-20_235519809-768x373.png 768w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-20_235519809-1536x747.png 1536w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image_2023-02-20_235519809.png 1903w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<h4 class="wp-block-heading">Import WhatsApp &amp; SMS contacts</h4>



<p>To import WhatsApp contacts or SMS contacts, Set the source to WhatsApp contacts or Phone (For SMS), Set the country code, and upload a .csv or .xlsx file. The &#8216;More Options&#8217; option allows you to set a custom field or add a tag to the contacts. </p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="500" src="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image-7-1024x500.png" alt="" class="wp-image-2743" srcset="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image-7-1024x500.png 1024w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image-7-300x146.png 300w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image-7-768x375.png 768w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image-7-1536x750.png 1536w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image-7.png 1850w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1024" height="494" src="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image-8-1024x494.png" alt="" class="wp-image-2744" srcset="https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image-8-1024x494.png 1024w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image-8-300x145.png 300w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image-8-768x371.png 768w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image-8-1536x742.png 1536w, https://docs.chatrace.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/image-8.png 1870w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>
]]></content:encoded>
					
